        "timestamp": "2019-10-15 12:58:38.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> So this is going to apply abbrev to ALL the decisions, including the non-Monitoring applications.\n\nTrue, if another application includes this parameter it will abbreviate.\nI'll fix this",
